{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Recommended: Pure AppKit + SwiftUI Settings推荐：纯 AppKit + SwiftUI 设置\n      Architecture: AppDelegate-driven lifecycle, NSWindow for progress, SwiftUI only for Settings view架构：由 AppDelegate 驱动的生命周期，使用 NSWindow 显示进度，SwiftUI 仅用于设置视图\n      \n        \n          Pros  优点\n          \n            Full control over window lifecycle (hide/show/close without quit)完全控制窗口生命周期（隐藏/显示/关闭而不退出）\n            NSPanel for progress popup — native, lightweight, auto-dismiss用于进度弹窗的 NSPanel — 原生、轻量、自动关闭\n            Proven pattern for \"agent\" apps (no Dock, no Menu Bar)经验证的“代理”应用模式（无 Dock、无菜单栏）\n            Easiest to handle \"relaunch = show settings\" behavior最容易处理“重新启动 = 显示设置”的行为\n          \n        \n        \n          Cons  缺点\n          \n            More AppKit boilerplate vs pure SwiftUI更多 AppKit 样板代码 vs 纯 SwiftUI\n            Two UI paradigms (AppKit windows + SwiftUI views)两种 UI 范式（AppKit 窗口 + SwiftUI 视图）","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1774718704180}
